(1132, 'KIC', NULL, 'David Fiedler', 'President', 'LCMS Foundation', 'Lutheran, Anglican & Reformed Denomination Leadership', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'low', true, 50, NULL, 'Over 25 years of service to LCMS including leading the LCMS Foundation since 2013 focused on donor engagement and stewardship. Longtime LCMS staffer (25+ years at headquarters) dedicated to ''serving the Lord through support provided to the Missouri Synod,'' leading fundraising and stewardship for LCMS ministries. Lay leader with deep confessional Lutheran background and major responsibility for resourcing denominational ministries.', 'Lay leader with deep confessional Lutheran background and major responsibility for resourcing denominational ministries.', 'Longtime LCMS staffer (25+ years at headquarters) dedicated to ''serving the Lord through support provided to the Missouri Synod,'' leading fundraising and stewardship for LCMS ministries.', NULL, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'Over 25 years of service to LCMS including leading the LCMS Foundation since 2013 focused on donor engagement and stewardship.', NULL, '["https://reporter.lcms.org/2013/fiedler-named-president-of-lcms-foundation/", "https://www.lcmsfoundation.org/about-us/our-leadership", "https://reporter.lcms.org/2017/fiedler-begin-second-five-year-term-foundation-president/"]'::jsonb),
