(1177, 'KIC', NULL, 'Christian Bateson', 'Owner', 'Resolute Services', 'Regional Chain Owners & Specialty CPG', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'low', true, 46, NULL, 'Acquired and scaled a construction services business projected to hit $7.5M revenue in 2024 following personal struggles. Public testimony highlighting faith as central to his turnaround, stating the acquisition ''rescued him from the depths'' in a story framed around redemption. Active marketplace leader with concrete faith testimony and demonstrated turnaround expertise; low mainstream profile despite meaningful business impact.', 'Active marketplace leader with concrete faith testimony and demonstrated turnaround expertise; low mainstream profile despite meaningful business impact.', 'Public testimony highlighting faith as central to his turnaround, stating the acquisition ''rescued him from the depths'' in a story framed around redemption.', NULL, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'Acquired and scaled a construction services business projected to hit $7.5M revenue in 2024 following personal struggles.', NULL, '["https://acquiringminds.co/articles/christian-bateson-resolute-services"]'::jsonb),
