(1208, 'KIC', NULL, 'Ron Blue', 'Founder and Chairman Emeritus, Blue Trust', 'Kingdom Advisors', 'Christian Finance & Investment Leaders', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'low', true, 43, NULL, 'Ron Blue is one of the most influential figures in the history of Christian financial planning and stewardship. He founded Ronald Blue and Co. in 1979, which grew into one of the largest fee-only Christian financial advisory firms in the United States, managing billions in assets. He is the author of more than 20 books on biblical financial principles, including Master Your Money and Splitting Heirs, which have sold millions of copies and shaped how generations of Christians think about wealth, generosity, and stewardship. Blue co-founded the Kingdom Advisors network, an organization training financial advisors to integrate biblical wisdom into their practice, which now serves thousands of Christian financial professionals globally. His decades of work building the infrastructure of Christian financial stewardship make him one of the most consequential figures in the faith-and-finance space.', 'Founding visionary of faith-driven wealth management industry with decades of influence on Christian financial stewardship.', 'Pioneering biblically based financial planning, with ''Blue Trust advisors apply biblical wisdom and technical expertise'' per their site.', NULL, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'Pioneer of biblically-based wealth management serving over 11,000 clients and authoring seminal works on Christian finance.', NULL, '["https://kingdomadvisors.com/about", "https://www.bluetrust.com/about/history/", "https://faithdriveninvestor.org/top-advisors-copy/", "https://careersatblue.com/blog/ron-blue-the-founder-of-blue-co"]'::jsonb),
(1209, 'KIC', NULL, 'Roma Downey', 'Actress, producer', NULL, 'christian_creators_arts', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'low', true, 43, NULL, 'Roma Downey is an Emmy-nominated actress and producer best known for her starring role as Monica in the CBS series Touched by an Angel, which ran for nine seasons from 1994 to 2003 and reached over 30 million weekly viewers at its peak. She is a devout Catholic and co-founder of LightWorkers Media with her husband Mark Burnett, through which she has produced some of the most-watched Christian media projects in television history, including The Bible miniseries in 2013, which became the most-watched cable miniseries in a decade, and the feature film Son of God. Downey has used her entertainment platform consistently to bring faith-centered storytelling to mainstream audiences, making her one of the most influential Christian figures in Hollywood.', 'Prominent Christian performer and producer with decades of faith-centered storytelling influence.', 'Long career in faith-based television; public Christian witness through roles in angel-themed and biblical content; co-produced *The Bible* miniseries', NULL, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'Starred in *Touched by an Angel* and co-produced *The Bible* miniseries with Mark Burnett', NULL, '["https://parade.com/news/touched-by-an-angel-icon-roma-downey-65-platinum-blonde-beauty-aging-in-reverse", "https://www.remindmagazine.com/article/36721/roma-downey-touched-by-an-angel-where-now/", "https://www.tvinsider.com/1225341/roma-downey-touched-by-an-angel-where-now/", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roma_Downey"]'::jsonb),
(1210, 'KIC', NULL, 'Jonathan Roumie', 'Lead actor, portraying Jesus Christ in *The Chosen*', 'The Chosen', 'christian_creators_arts', 'Los Angeles, California', NULL, NULL, 'low', true, 43, NULL, 'Jonathan Roumie is an actor best known for his portrayal of Jesus Christ in The Chosen, the independently produced multi-season series about the life of Jesus that has become the most-watched Christian media project in history, with over 600 million views across 180 countries. Roumie is a devout Catholic who has spoken extensively about how the role transformed his own prayer life and faith. Beyond acting, he is a lay Catholic minister and advocate for the Hallow prayer app, which reached No. 1 in the App Store after he promoted it. His unique position as the face of the most widely viewed portrayal of Jesus in history, combined with his genuine personal faith, makes him one of the most culturally significant Christian public figures of the current era.', 'Active on Instagram @jonroumie — he engages with fans and faith communities directly. Contact through The Chosen''s official channels (thechosen.tv) for partnership inquiries. Roumie is passionate about serving faith communities — a GCU Chosen screening event followed by a Q&A with Roumie is a low-cost, high-impact entry point that doesn''t require a large speaking fee. His Catholic faith also means the GCU evangelical audience is a slight stretch — frame as broadly Christian.

Contact: 📍 MAILING ADDRESS: The Chosen: 2900 W. Quincy Avenue, Littleton, CO 80120 | thechosen.tv | Instagram: @jonroumie

The Chosen official: thechosen.tv. Representation through talent agencies (CAA or similar). Speaking through faith-based speaker bureaus. Active on Instagram and social media @jonroumie.', 'Public Christian testimony; chosen for role specifically to portray Jesus in faith-based series', 'No direct GCU connection documented. The Chosen has an enormous viewership among GCU''s student demographic. A Jonathan Roumie chapel appearance or GCU-The Chosen event partnership would be one of the most viral and high-impact engagements GCU could create — especially with GCU''s large Catholic and evangelical student population.', '[]'::jsonb, '[{"date": "2026", "title": "The Chosen official website \u2014 700M+ global views, Jonathan Roumie as Jesus", "source": "thechosen.tv", "url": "https://thechosen.tv"}, {"date": "2026", "title": "Jonathan Roumie Wikipedia \u2014 born Jun 1, 1978 New York City. Catholic actor, The Chosen star.", "source": "Wikipedia", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Roumie"}]'::jsonb, 'Lead actor portraying Jesus Christ in breakthrough faith-based television series *The Chosen*', 'Dear Jonathan,

I''m reaching out from Grand Canyon University — the largest Christian university in America. The Chosen has deeply impacted our campus community.

Would you be open to a brief call with President Brian Mueller?

With deep respect,
[Name] | Grand Canyon University | [Phone]', '["https://thechosen.tv", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Roumie"]'::jsonb),
